Adam Busch https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Adam_Busch 0 Adam Richard Busch (born July 6, 1978) is an American actor, film director and singer best known starring as Warren Mears on the television series Buffy the Vampire Slayer. He also starred as Neal in the TBS comedy Men at Work. He appears in the webshow MyMusic on YouTube as Indie.
